gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 132, Suns 121
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Victor Wembanyamas 38 points and 10 rebounds, the Spurs defeated the Suns, 132-121. Zach Collins added 19 points, eight rebounds and four assists for the Spurs in the victory, while Devin Booker (31 points, nine rebounds, 13 assists) and Kevin Durant (28 points, six rebounds) combined for 59 points for the Suns in the losing effort. The Spurs improve to 3-2 on the season, while the Suns fall to 2-3.
